&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY JOIN ALO?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mindful movement. It’s at the core of why we do what we do at ALO—it’s our calling. Because mindful movement in the studio leads to better living. It changes who yogis are off the mat, making their lives and their communities better. That’s the real meaning of studio-to-street: taking the consciousness from practice on the mat and putting it into practice in life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are&amp;nbsp;seeking&amp;nbsp;a motivated and technically strong&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Computer Science Intern – Product Information Management (PIM)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;to join our Biz Tech Operations&amp;nbsp;team. This internship offers a unique opportunity to design and build a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;foundational Product Information Management (PIM) capability&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; that will serve as a single, trusted source of product data across ALO’s technology ecosystem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Today, product information is distributed across multiple systems—including&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;NGC PLM,&amp;nbsp;FDM4&amp;nbsp;ERP,&amp;nbsp;FDM4&amp;nbsp;WMS, Shopify&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;, and spreadsheets—resulting in duplicated integrations, inconsistent data, and manual workarounds. As an intern, you will help design and implement a centralized PIM solution built on ALO’s &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;data lake (Amazon Redshift)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;and supporting data pipelines, enabling all downstream systems, services, and teams to reliably source product data from a single platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This work will create a scalable foundation that can be expanded over time with additional product attributes, governance, and automation to support ALO’s continued growth and tech environment expansion.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;The ALO internship programs starts June 8th and ends July 31st. Interns will be working 40 hours a week at our Beverly Hills HQ.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
